title: Kendall Jenner shows off her chest
text: comments Kendall Jenner has said many times in the past that she loves to go bra free and show off her nipples. So it's not much of a surprise that the 21-year-old model was showing off her chest again on Saturday. The Keeping Up With The Kardashians star looked perky as she posed in a black sheer top for an image shared to social media. Risque business: Kendall Jenner wore a see-through top while promoting her new clothing line with Kylie on Saturday Even more: Here the daughter of Kris Jenner is looking at the camera The beauty was posing in an outdoor/indoor setting. The E! princess had on a white jacket and matching slacks that were gathered at the waist. Silver pointy heels were hardly noticeable. Out in the Bib Apple: Also on Saturday the pinup was seen in NYC wearing casual attire Ta-da: The star had on a Louis Vuitton T-shirt, a brown suede jacket and high-waisted jeans with bell bottoms Walk on the wild side: The ex of Harry Styles had on boots that were zip up and made from beige snakeskin The clothes are for her new line Kendall + Kylie collection. 'DropOne coming soon | #KKspring17 now available Shop Now â†“ shop.kendall-kylie.com,' she wrote on the site she shares with her sister Kylie, 19. Also on Saturday the pinup was seen in NYC wearing casual attire. The star had on a Louis Vuitton T-shirt, a brown suede jacket and high-waisted jeans with bell bottoms. The ex of Harry Styles had on boots that were zip up and made from beige snakeskin. KUWKendall? It appeared that a camera man was behind her as she stepped off a sidewalk
